{"tid":213524,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實班細路幾可愛，不過我都唔知隻雀最終會係點","createTime":"2017-04-23T07:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T13:14:35.000Z","uid":43264,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66a8f84496fa0e3e821d3bd8a037052fe39d4884","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6du70jH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6du70jH.jpg&h=2e9ef333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先响公司樓下個公園有班細路見到隻飛唔起既雀，佢地圍住隻雀擾攘左一輪，其中一個跟手就捉住隻雀，然後佢地就開始研究。<br />\n<br />\n最初佢地成班講既係唔知咩話黎，我埋去問「你地識唔識講廣東話架？」跟住佢地好開心咁話識，忽然就轉晒廣東話channel，流利程度令我聯想起講「屌你個非洲呀，我巴西架碌柒！」果個細路，所以我無問佢地係咪印巴。<br />\n<br />\n佢地之後既研究內容，就係圍繞住點樣處理隻雀，主要當然係諗住救佢啦，D細路總有一種覺得自己可以拯救生命既幻想。不過我見個細路捉到隻雀硬晒軚，都估到隻雀擺唔耐架喇。後來班細路仲想學D電影咁，抛隻雀上半空等佢忽然翻生自己飛走。我就梗係叫住佢地唔好啦，可以想像到，佢一抛起隻雀，班細路we嘩鬼叫咁散開，跟住隻雀攤返落地，死埋，跟住其他細路就會一齊屌鳩抛雀果個整死隻雀。<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好話D細路係咁，就算大人，都總會以為人人都可以成為英雄，然後又會屌鳩一D你諗住佢會成為英雄但係最終唔成功既人。"},{"pid":"2ac9b23e43e74642cc7a5dce02986e930715e5b0","tid":213524,"uid":23785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8b72a8592bec716cfe9adccb44b41f0ef8019a","tid":213524,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:40:51.000Z","msg":"最尾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92919af3148ba171e781782508246e3e608ddf51","tid":213524,"uid":47099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"禽流感"},{"pid":"bbd896843e5bef5cb8120bf7334c0a35b21571ee","tid":213524,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"生命教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc183780fc0794a9625f61dfc65c45fa2d1da6f0","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住我走左啦，呢D通常玩好耐，我臨走叫佢地要抛都抛去花糟，跌得無咁傷。"},{"pid":"8e17c528dbd833183f83da097780bcbafe2177bc","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禽流感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚驚地，我feel到自己有D喉嚨很乾既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43efd3e81c00a50e9d8baa0314cf5c683581a9df","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生命教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教唔到D咩⋯亦學唔到D咩⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be3f2448796dca7d3c028fff9a10d7b807db652","tid":213524,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84ff3ba3f5cec077100c9001b94e8cf945e9cc14","tid":213524,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:22:30.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d834a7dc0ca1d45410ca46b02821007d7f457f9","tid":213524,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:25:21.000Z","msg":"心地好過好多連登仔"},{"pid":"2fee6ef95e7fc34a8e643bf10d6397885ba17005","tid":213524,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心地好過好多連登仔</blockquote><br />\n拎幾歲細路同連登仔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0b1ffa12e83682ab4f64c32317bcebeee54cf0","tid":213524,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"飛唔起既雀應該本身都就快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma