gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001cb1d180ea160338829233667024c7a709bb7e","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>心地好過好多連登仔</blockquote><br />\n拎幾歲細路同連登仔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大部分連登仔唔係幾歲細路咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該好多係精蟲階段，或者被精蟲操控大腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2535ce91f8e926559cae3a7692958588e5d12e","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生命教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教唔到D咩⋯亦學唔到D咩⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔一定既，睇佢自己有冇思考姐<br />\n<br />\n就算係細路，都總有少少感覺既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能佢抛隻雀上天撻返落黎整死左隻雀之後會上左癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effc0a573ac443ffb5216b495478a4d3ca222ca2","tid":213524,"uid":38462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>禽流感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚驚地，我feel到自己有D喉嚨很乾既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5baa24b353b6a9e760b8125f53aeae1cd56fd9d5","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拋死佢都算係解脫 安樂死好多人想都唔做得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我最後講既，好多人都覺得自己可以成為英雄，覺得自己可以拯救生命，決定人地條路點行先係最好。<br />\n<br />\n我以前有個fd，响大陸長駐做野，識左條女，本身條女做美容之類既，佢就話人地人地份工好慘要受氣，比錢人學英文同會計，叫人辭左本身份工，屌那星好似英文同會計係三個月學成咁話學就識，學完就變左上等人做野唔洗睇人面色咁。結果最終條女就梗係學唔掂，佢就話人地又是蠢又懶，到最後咪又係散左。我就問佢，屌你你份工好撚高尚好撚唔洗受氣既咩？我問佢做乜唔辭左份工去考返個醫生律師牌返黎？佢自己都覺得自己戇鳩。"},{"pid":"934a766dccc77e0718873e14f0bd4d90d1817e07","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>禽流感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n驚驚地，我feel到自己有D喉嚨很乾既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2967dd6f56b110bc80a9f629a43ae8ce588cb0","tid":213524,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拋死佢都算係解脫 安樂死好多人想都唔做得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n動物好少求死"},{"pid":"a045328667da5c2ec76d71813e5c69af6edb0255","tid":213524,"uid":34954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>拋死佢都算係解脫 安樂死好多人想都唔做得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我最後講既，好多人都覺得自己可以成為英雄，覺得自己可以拯救生命，決定人地條路點行先係最好。<br />\n<br />\n我以前有個fd，响大陸長駐做野，識左條女，本身條女做美容之類既，佢就話人地人地份工好慘要受氣，比錢人學英文同會計，叫人辭左本身份工，屌那星好似英文同會計係三個月學成咁話學就識，學完就變左上等人做野唔洗睇人面色咁。結果最終條女就梗係學唔掂，佢就話人地又是蠢又懶，到最後咪又係散左。我就問佢，屌你你份工好撚高尚好撚唔洗受氣既咩？我問佢做乜唔辭左份工去考返個醫生律師牌返黎？佢自己都覺得自己戇鳩。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都俾你用一個小故事總結<br />\n巴打好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7e96c47b1a41ee0e9ecb1080a14a8b3a134d93","tid":213524,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>突然諗番起一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人/細路 實望一望就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:我都無咁好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要反省下</blockquote><br />\n老母一句有禽流感就拉走個仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n莫講話禽流感，街度見到狗都唔比個仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識個朋友屋企全部寵物都係執/領養返嚟"},{"pid":"b859421aded30b88fd3c839da86fa5a972588e6a","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>拋死佢都算係解脫 安樂死好多人想都唔做得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n動物好少求死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左街市D海鮮，佢地一個二個成日用懇求既眼神望住我，同我講「食我啦主人！！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3981d3e7464bd2f8633cca96dcbd683b96bdfbd8","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>拋死佢都算係解脫 安樂死好多人想都唔做得</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我最後講既，好多人都覺得自己可以成為英雄，覺得自己可以拯救生命，決定人地條路點行先係最好。<br />\n<br />\n我以前有個fd，响大陸長駐做野，識左條女，本身條女做美容之類既，佢就話人地人地份工好慘要受氣，比錢人學英文同會計，叫人辭左本身份工，屌那星好似英文同會計係三個月學成咁話學就識，學完就變左上等人做野唔洗睇人面色咁。結果最終條女就梗係學唔掂，佢就話人地又是蠢又懶，到最後咪又係散左。我就問佢，屌你你份工好撚高尚好撚唔洗受氣既咩？我問佢做乜唔辭左份工去考返個醫生律師牌返黎？佢自己都覺得自己戇鳩。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都俾你用一個小故事總結<br />\n巴打好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b3e02ac57a6b9b7cfd821bfdfb1bb212e2a4e","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>突然諗番起一拳超人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人/細路 實望一望就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:我都無咁好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要反省下</blockquote><br />\n老母一句有禽流感就拉走個仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n莫講話禽流感，街度見到狗都唔比個仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識個朋友屋企全部寵物都係執/領養返嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔爭在領養埋我，我無禽流感同瘋狗症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708db4d69bc6d57b5540eb40922613c72a167e3d","tid":213524,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50972e53d2c9ee9432a998f15912300deaab03a9","tid":213524,"uid":9880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"係咪咕菇固黎架?"},{"pid":"c7e8d557fe26546e59b39cc082aaa578fdaa76d6","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪咕菇固黎架?</blockquote><br />\n唔係灰鳩黎架咩？？睇佢個樣灰鳩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50abac246318d9364015ce8bf310735a47b093c5","tid":213524,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35bbdecd695954abb91594ca7cd6e44121e7fdf","tid":213524,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁都有寓意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n似啲中小學短文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d9f756eec9f49fb146ba0dbffcf136e882fd6","tid":213524,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img